Observation - Class in event
Observation is the class that extends the Event_Simulation abstract class and has the purpose of distinguish different types of events.
Observation(ISimulation) - Constructor for class event.Observation
Class Observation constructor to be called when the event is created in simulation time 0.
Observation(ISimulation, double) - Constructor for class event.Observation
Class Observation constructor to be called at a given time in the simulation.
Obstacles - Class in map
Class Obstacles is used has a wrapper to store the obstacles coordinates to be processed by the map constructor x - X coordinate of the obstacle y - Y coordinate of the obstacle
Obstacles(int, int) - Constructor for class map.Obstacles
Class Obstacle constructor.
